<div class="content-page">
  <p class="page-intro">Games should be fun, not frustrating. No ads, no sign-ups, no dark patterns.</p>

  <h2>Zero Ads</h2>
  <p>No banner ads, no interstitials, no video ads. The game loads and you play.</p>

  <h2>No Tracking</h2>
  <p>No analytics, no cookies, no fingerprinting. We don't know who you are and we don't want to.</p>

  <h2>Local Saves</h2>
  <p>Your progress, high scores, and favorites are saved locally in your browser. They never leave your device.</p>

  <h2>Lots of Games</h2>
  <p>Puzzle, arcade, card, board, word, strategy, and more. All playable right in your browser — nothing to download or install.</p>

  <h2>Dark Mode</h2>
  <p>Respects your system preference or toggle manually. Easy on the eyes for late-night sessions.</p>

  <h2>Mobile Friendly</h2>
  <p>Most games work on phones and tablets. Games that need a keyboard are clearly marked.</p>

  <h2>Fast Search</h2>
  <p>Find any game instantly. Filter by category, letter, or just start typing a name.</p>

  <h2>100+ Languages</h2>
  <p>Translated into over 100 languages so everyone can play, wherever they are.</p>
</div>
